 font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">In his&nbsp;<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7mXgLMpG3m/?igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">social media post</a>&nbsp;announcing the buzzy item, Reynolds wrote, “Years from now they will look back at 2024 as the year the War of the Popcorn Buckets began.”</font></p><div data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/sharethrough@published" class="ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1" data-placement="{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:5},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:3}}" data-unselectable="true" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 849.333px; overflow: hidden; font-size: medium;"><div data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published" class="ad-slot" data-path="end/ad-slot-dynamic[0]/items" data-desktop-slot-id="ad_nat_btf_01" data-mobile-slot-id="ad_nat_btf_01" data-unselectable="true" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 849.333px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;"><div class="ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container" style="box-sizing: