 data-analytics-observe="off" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">The first round of 2024 bucket battles, one might argue, was won in March by a “Dune: Part Two” popcorn&nbsp;<a href="https://x.com/AMCTheatres/status/1763044153758220593" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">bucket</a>&nbsp;so strange it spawned a&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rl_Xhvgkxrk" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">“Saturday Night Live” skit</a>).<span style="color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest);">The appeal of these buckets – also referred to as “concession vessels” or even “</span><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/05/25/business/why-do-we-eat-popcorn-at-the-movies/index.html" style="font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">Collectible Concession Vehicles</a><span style="color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest);">” to include specialty beverage containers and the like – is wide, attracting both seasoned collectors and casual movie fans.</span></font></p><div data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/outstream@published" class="ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1" data-placement="{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:7},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:6}}" data-unselectable="true" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 849.333px; overflow: hidden; font-size: medium;"><div class="ad-slot-dynamic__close" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 18px; height: 18px; opacity: 0.3; cursor: pointer;"></div></div><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv6awlu00033d5vpv3x95ip@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="on" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">“Seeing an item at the movie theater of my favorite characters draws me in,” said collector&nbsp;<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@shahjiadam?_t=8mnOCrfrcY3&amp;_r=1" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">Shahji Adam</a>&nbsp;in an email to CNN. Adam, who also collects other pop culture products like Funko Pop figures, described his passion for popcorn buckets as “fun nostalgia” for items that help him remember the feeling of watching a particular movie for the first time.</font></p><div class="teads-adCall" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium;"></div><h2 class="subheader" data-editable="text" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/clwv6nqw7000g3d5vqa86zaiq@published" data-component-name="subheader" id="a-brief-history-of-the-bucket" data-article-gutter="true" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--theme-subheader__font-weight); clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">A brief history of the bucket</font></h2><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv6oogo000j3d5v0j4vsyrm@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="on" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">Branded popcorn buckets began&nbsp;<a href="https://dvcshop.com/a-brief-history-of-disney-popcorn-buckets/#:~:text=The%20First%20Disney%20Parks%20Popcorn%20Bucket&amp;text=The%20sought%20after%20character%20buckets,featuring%20the%20latest%20popular%20titles." target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">popping up in the 1990s</a>&nbsp;at Disney theme parks before they made their way to theaters in marketing campaigns.</font></p><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv6jm7i00073d5vxd6t8ul2@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="on" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">AMC’s Nels Storm, vice president of food &amp; beverage strategy and leader of the merchandise team, points to 2019 as a turning point in the novelty concession vessel’s evolution.</font></p><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv6jwsi000a3d5v2425geeb@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="on" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">“We experimented with versions of plastic popcorn tubs and beverage vessels with film branding for years. The real inception of the current program kicked off in 2019 when we introduced the R2-D2 vessel to the movie-going public,” Storm said, in reference to the famous android-shaped popcorn containers that came out in support of that year’s “Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker.”</font></p><aside data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/twitter/instances/clwvdh32u000d3d5v9pdvqlvk@published" class="twitter" data-editable="settings" data-article-gutter="true" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw); font-size: medium;"><blockquote class="twitter__tweet" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 540px; margin: 1em auto;"><div class="twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; max-width: 550px; width: 540px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><iframe id="twitter-widget-0" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true" class="" title="X Post" src="https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;%3D%3D&amp;frame=false&amp