ry-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">Since then, other in-demand popcorn buckets have included the Ghostbusters Ecto-1 car, Thor’s hammer Mjölnir, Dominic Toretto’s Charger, the Wonka hat and a Barbie car, Storm said.</font></p><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv6zqn1000s3d5vv9m2ybgw@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="on" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">AMC even recently brought back the R2-D2 popcorn bucket for this year’s&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cnn.com/cnn-underscored/deals/may-4th-star-wars-day-deals-2024" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">May the Fourth “Star Wars” Day</a>, in support of the rerelease of “<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/05/03/entertainment/star-wars-phantom-menace-turns-25/index.html" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace</a>.”</font></p><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwv701gc000u3d5vncf5ipss@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="off" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-536px + 49vw);"><font face="Comic Sans MS">That bucket is Adam’s favorite, as seen on his&nbsp;<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@shahjiadam/video/7364808167626165547?_r=1&amp;_t=8mnOCrfrcY3" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size--from-small); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small);">TikTok</a>.</font></p><p class="paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph-primary-core-light" data-uri="cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/clwvetn2o000q3d5vm60p7w86@published" data-editable="text" data-component-name="paragraph" data-article-gutter="true" data-analytics-observe="off" style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); color: var(--style-type-primary-1-highest); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; 